title: This Place is Awful!!
body: i took my son here and he died!!! I will eat your burgers no more!!!! My cat also died and my house burnt down. I have diarrhea and migraines and i cant feel any of my limbs..... i have been hospitalized and my wife left me!!

ownersResponse.body: Hi Bob! I’m sorry to hear that! I hope he gets better soon. You and your remaining family are entitled to a free pack of breadsticks on your next visit. Check your email for the coupon code!

title: terrible, what happened??
body: I used to go here back in the day all the time. What happened? the food quality is really bad, and there's a weird stink coming from the locked back room, and there's this gross darkish liquid near it. I'd much rather eat at mcwonalds at this point!

title: Wretched, terrible, disgusting place
body: I've had the absolute worst parts of my life in this disgusting establishment. I think the world would be better if this place spontaneously burst into flames. God willing I will never see this place or you ever again.

title: Good stuff!
body: Brought the family here to relax! The service was terrific and the yogurt is like nothing else in this town! Lots of memories made here!

title: Great food! Kids loved it
body: Took my kids here for a birthday party. The town never had a McWonalds so this was a new experience for us! We only had that other burger place but its quality has been going down for a while.

title: Tasteless chicken, just bad
body: title says all

title: lowkey poisonous
body: I'm pretty sure this is where my diahrrea came from!!!

title: energizing!
body: Almost as good as the sweet, sweet electrolytes. Doktor enjoyed it as well!

title: What am I even eating?!
body: This institution has got to be one of the most putrid I've ever been to, not to mention their "food". I sincerely hope the owners have plans to renovate the exterior and change most if not all of the recipes. I will not be dining here again!

title: HUGE FAN OF THE SPEED
body: Everything is SPEEDY in this place, I LOVE IT!

title: great atmosphere
body: The cold, metallic atmosphere is something I dig. The excessive number of vents is also a plus!

title: Quite ze treat
body: Not only do I think ze yogurt taste good, but I also ran some tests and found it one of ze healthiest food created!

ownersResponse.body: Thank you, I can always rely on the medic!

title: it could maybe pick up the pace
body: The food's not half bad, but the waiters and the serving time...it's giving me the itch just waiting

ownersResponse.body: Very sorry sir. Please accept this 20% off coupon the next time you eat at this establishment. Cheers.

title: !HIGHLY INEDIBLE, STAY AWAY!
body: My kids and I fell really ill trying out its specialty, the Chumburger. Plus it didn't even taste good!

title: A trip down memory lane
body: This reminds me of how it used to be, before the wars. Good, good times...

title: sus drinks
body: their soft drinks honestly taste SUSpicious

title: It's filthy in zerr, ugh.
body: I may not have my own medical license, but zis place is even worse than my clinic!

title: Innovative machines, I find them quaint.
body: Their public display of soda-creation is quite the spectacle!

title: Did this even pass the edibility test?
body: You know, ever since I saw what they were serving, I wondered if my cybernetic organs can even digest them.

title: It's simply bland
body: From the food, to the atmosphere, to the decor, they all just seem so bland and uninteresting.

title: SO BAD
body: ahahahahah my wife would've absolutely hated this
